<br>
Thankfully, Firiona Vie opened up, and I started a cleric and couldn't be happier.  Logged on my druid one day on the old server, /boggled at the sheer amount of ooc and shouted gibberish, and have not been back since.  Even if I had not left that server, I am almost certain I wouldn't be playing a druid any more.  I miss the soloing abilities quite often, and miss the travel aspect somewhat less, but I like being wanted in groups so much more.<br>
<br>
